l 1/f noise mechanisms, carrier number and mobility fluctuations,\nmust be considered simultaneously to properly understand the low frequency\nnoise in graphene FETs. The proposed analytical compact model can be easily\nimplemented and integrated in circuit simulators, which can be of high\nimportance for graphene based circuits design.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jun 2018 10:42:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Oct 2018 09:32:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-22"}
